{"tid":1883613,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"太古城確診男子 與同事日前曾到醫管局總部開會","createTime":"2020-02-17T05:32:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T05:43:49.000Z","uid":227801,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"07fcb5b6d627bc7b6413571a8a1837f3791aa810","tid":1883613,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:32:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509013-20200217.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509013-20200217.htm&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQ9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=fa632097\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509013-20200217.htm&h=41f26b47\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509013-20200217.htm</a><br />\n消息指，本港再多一人，初步對新型冠狀病毒測試呈陽性反應，病人是一名45歲男子，目前正在伊利沙伯醫院留醫，相信他與昨天住在太古城的54歲確診男子個案有關。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，兩人是同事，日前曾到醫管局總部開會，醫管局已在相關地點進行消毒清洗。"},{"pid":"a6a792980ff8eed97c7a251cf7d6ae332106a49a","tid":1883613,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee2b03c0918aeed4abd6a22e0b3c32e992268404","tid":1883613,"uid":295548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T05:38:37.000Z","msg":"《天滅中共賦》<br />\n<br />\n共黨臣民 作惡多端<br />\n外侵諸邦 內屠義士<br />\n赤匪所至 寸草不生<br />\n禍國殃民 血債累累<br />\n習妖維尼 逆天而行<br />\n自立為帝 天怒人怨<br />\n庚子伊始 天譴將臨<br />\n大仙報夢 國運已盡<br />\n共黨治下 必有七患<br />\n正月武肺 播毒中原<br />\n二月流感 飛禽盡亡<br />\n三月地震 血流成河<br />\n四月豬瘟 百物騰升<br />\n五月飢荒 易子而食<br />\n六月內戰 析骸而爨<br />\n七月水災 長江決堤<br />\n炎共將亡 水德當立<br />\n歲在庚子 暴政必亡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uCW3BCS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuCW3BCS.jpg&h=64a71671&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de9e9a2907bdc45f7d897d188611c5f3141301aa","tid":1883613,"uid":155682,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"c